component_description: Detection results for Power-Ups Section > Streak Freeze

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Streak Freeze > Icon
elements.description: Light blue ice crystal or frozen droplet icon positioned at the left side of the first power-up row
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly encloses the ice crystal icon with minimal excess space and good alignment.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Streak Freeze > Title
elements.description: Bold black text 'Streak Freeze' to the right of the ice crystal icon
elements.explanation: Bounding box properly contains the 'Streak Freeze' title, with only slight excess space at the right.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Streak Freeze > Description
elements.description: Gray text describing functionality that reads 'Streak Freeze allows your streak to remain in place for one full day of inactivity'
elements.explanation: Box accurately covers the entire description text, with a small amount of padding above and below.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Streak Freeze > Status Indicator
elements.description: Small green pill-shaped badge with white text '2/2 EQUIPPED' indicating full usage of this power-up
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely fits the pill badge and its text, showing high accuracy.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Streak Freeze > Equipped Button
elements.description: Light gray pill-shaped button with lighter gray text 'EQUIPPED' indicating this power-up is currently active
elements.explanation: Box tightly frames the 'EQUIPPED' button with excellent horizontal and vertical fitting.

component_description: Detection results for App Header Bar > Status Bar

elements.label: App Header Bar > Status Bar > Time
elements.description: White text '9:41' displayed in the top-left corner of the screen against the green header background
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly and accurately encloses the '9:41' text with minimal extra padding.

elements.label: App Header Bar > Status Bar > Network Indicator
elements.description: White cellular signal strength icon positioned in the top-right area of the screen
elements.explanation: Original box is too wide and partially overlaps other status icons; suggested box more tightly fits the cellular icon.

elements.label: App Header Bar > Status Bar > WiFi Indicator
elements.description: White WiFi signal icon positioned in the top-right area of the screen, between the network indicator and battery icon
elements.explanation: Original box covers multiple status icons; suggested coordinates tightly fit only the WiFi indicator.

elements.label: App Header Bar > Status Bar > Battery Indicator
elements.description: White battery icon showing full charge positioned at the far top-right corner of the screen
elements.explanation: Box accurately encloses the battery icon with only minor excess width.

component_description: Detection results for App Header Bar

elements.label: App Header Bar > Progress Bar
elements.description: Bright green horizontal bar spanning the full width at the top of the screen, containing the app's counters and indicators
elements.explanation: Bounding box matches the header bar almost perfectly, only minor pixel overhang at the bottom.

elements.label: App Header Bar > Fire Token Counter
elements.description: Flame icon with the number '1' in white, positioned on the left side of the green header bar
elements.explanation: Box accurately frames the fire token counter, slight extra padding on the bottom/right but very close fit.

elements.label: App Header Bar > Gem Counter
elements.description: Blue hexagonal gem icon with '505' in white text, centered in the green header bar
elements.explanation: Bounding box very tightly fits the gem counter, minimal excess space; nearly perfect annotation.

elements.label: App Header Bar > Hearts Counter
elements.description: Red heart icon with infinity symbol (âˆž) in white, positioned on the right side of the green header bar

component_description: Detection results for Power-Ups Section > Double or Nothing

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Double or Nothing > Icon
elements.description: Orange calendar-like icon with flame decoration and the number '7' inside, positioned at the left of the second power-up row
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly encompasses the orange calendar icon with the '7', with only a minor margin misalignment at the bottom right edge.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Double or Nothing > Title
elements.description: Bold black text 'Double or Nothing' to the right of the calendar icon
elements.explanation: Box covers the entire app window instead of the small title text. Tightened box around the 'Double or Nothing' text.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Double or Nothing > Description
elements.description: Gray text explaining 'Double your 50 gem wager by maintaining a 7 day streak' below the title
elements.explanation: Box accurately spans the multi-line gray description text, with correct top and bottom alignment. Left margin could be closer but is sufficiently accurate.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Double or Nothing > Purchase Button
elements.description: White pill-shaped button with text 'GET FOR:' and a blue gem icon with '50' indicating the purchase cost
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely frames the button, text, and icon with only minor top-bottom excess padding.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Title
elements.description: Bold black text 'Power-Ups' at the top of the white content area below the green header
elements.explanation: Original box covered almost the entire screen, not just the title text. Suggested a tight box around the label for accurate coverage.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Divider Line
elements.description: Thin horizontal gray line spanning the width of the screen below the 'Power-Ups' title
elements.explanation: Box was vertically offset and far too tall; suggested a much thinner and accurately placed bounding box over the gray divider line.

elements.label: Power-Ups Section > Divider Line 2
elements.description: Thin horizontal gray line separating the Streak Freeze power-up from the Double or Nothing power-up below
elements.explanation: Original box was centered but too short and limited in width; corrected to span the actual divider line's width and height.
